	y1[i] ~ dpois(mu1[i])
	y2[i] ~ dpois(mu2[i])

    ynew2[i] ~ dpois(mu2[i])

	for (k in 1:2) {

	}   
	# Spatial priors (CAR) for the shared random effects

	for (k in 1:2) {
		a0[k] ~ dflat() 
		# disease-specific  spatial precision
		
		sigma[k]~dunif(0,1)

	}                
		sigmaS~dunif(0,1)
